Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.33,0:00:03.88,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Flowing water has no form.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.88,0:00:05.65,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}A blowing wind can't be seen.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.65,0:00:07.65,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}All cases can be freely deduced!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.65,0:00:09.20,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}A very strange message!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.20,0:00:11.20,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Crush the trick and identify the killer!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.20,0:00:12.68,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}He sees the single truth for what it is,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.68,0:00:14.45,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}and looks like a kid but has the mind of an adult!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.45,0:00:16.43,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}His name? Detective Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.42,0:01:59.45,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}We went to the ice-skating rink at Tropical Land with Sonoko,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.45,0:02:02.31,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}who, as usual, was hunting for a boyfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.63,0:02:07.75,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}While skating, we met a group of five friends who were part of a clay shooting club.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.15,0:02:11.52,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}While we were waiting to watch the fireworks together,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.52,0:02:13.13,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}we heard a scream from Sonoko, who was in the restroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.56,0:02:22.22,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}When I went to see what's going on, what awaited me was...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.20,0:02:28.62,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}...the body of Chihiro Itami, with a shot in the chest from a shotgun.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.75,0:02:33.65,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}From the S written in blood next to the victim's body,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.65,0:02:35.68,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}the old man deduced that the killer had to be
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.68,0:02:38.86,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}the only person in the group whose name starts with S, Izumi Sano{\rHonorifics - Narration Off\be10}-san{\r\be10}, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.86,0:02:39.99,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think so!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.15,0:02:43.11,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.11,0:02:45.97,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,As you can tell by examining the body,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.97,0:02:49.71,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,the victim was shot in the chest and died instantly.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.71,0:02:55.06,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It wasn't possible for her to write something with her own blood after she was shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.18,0:02:57.12,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Afterwards, we discovered,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.12,0:03:00.23,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}along with the last number Chihiro tried to call on her cell phone,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.23,0:03:02.23,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}the letters KIX.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.36,0:03:05.87,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}KIX?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.74,0:03:09.97,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Wait, I've seen this somewhere before...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.35,0:03:28.65,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}KIX...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.65,0:03:30.44,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Where have I...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.44,0:03:32.00,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Mr. Detective...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.00,0:03:35.02,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,May we at least{\rHonorifics - Dialogue} chan{\r}ge into our shoes?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.02,0:03:36.97,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We came straight from the skating rink.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.95,0:03:41.70,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as you take a detective along.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.70,0:03:44.88,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But come right back.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.88,0:03:48.59,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Chiba{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}, will you please escort them?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.59,0:03:50.35,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.44,0:03:54.50,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, don't cry, Yoriko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.90,0:03:59.11,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,Yoriko Komatsu (30)\NHousewife
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.90,0:03:59.11,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,Izumi Sano (28)\NOffice Worker
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.82,0:03:58.58,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But Chihiro... Chihiro...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.11,0:04:03.07,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,Kunitomo Oda (29)\NFirefighter
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.11,0:04:03.07,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,Yasuharu Misawa (29)\NBanker
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.20,0:04:03.21,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Yoriko.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.14,0:04:07.07,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure the police will find the killer.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.48,0:04:14.35,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Idiot...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.43,0:04:17.02,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.02,0:04:21.40,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the same kind of phone the victim had, isn't it, Sonoko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-neechan{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.58,0:04:29.85,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me this kid thinks {\i1}I'm{\i0} the killer.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.87,0:04:35.93,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No! I just want to see your phone!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.93,0:04:36.72,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.27,0:04:42.27,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}. You shouldn't be fooling around with it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.27,0:04:47.77,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, Sonoko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-neechan{\r}, was it really the sound of a firework you heard?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.77,0:04:53.95,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, yeah! A whistle, and then an explosion...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.29,0:05:00.72,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Sonoko, you replaced your phone?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.97,0:05:02.88,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Something like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.88,0:05:05.34,Dialogue Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Locker Room
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.18,0:05:08.79,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}I've figured out the trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.79,0:05:12.81,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}But anybody could have done it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.12,0:05:16.35,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Maybe there's something in that weird comment...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.22,0:05:19.80,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yoriko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, pull yourself together.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.80,0:05:23.30,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry. It just reminds me of the accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.05,0:05:26.79,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yoriko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.79,0:05:28.71,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You were lucky, Izumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.71,0:05:32.87,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You weren't there when it happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.01,0:05:39.80,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I was sick with a cold, okay?\NIt's not like I was lucky.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.80,0:05:43.06,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,As of today, I'm quitting the club.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.06,0:05:45.81,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's like we've been cursed.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.81,0:05:50.00,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to die like Narita{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}, with a gun suddenly going off.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.24,0:05:55.98,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, enough small talk. Let's head back.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.98,0:05:57.20,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,R-Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.55,0:06:00.70,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}I see. So that's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.73,0:06:04.56,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}That's why he's the odd one out!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.70,0:06:08.58,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}But I still don't have proof.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.39,0:06:12.71,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}That message isn't enough to pin the crime on one person...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.32,0:06:22.60,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Two dark red dots...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.10,0:06:27.37,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Could it be?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.66,0:06:31.20,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.58,0:06:33.92,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.85,0:06:36.85,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.28,0:06:40.20,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.50,0:06:44.70,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.40,0:06:46.47,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.10,0:06:51.12,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}I found it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.78,0:06:56.59,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}This is it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.03,0:07:02.20,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}I've found it! This is solid proof!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.17,0:07:07.31,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}This proof will help me corner the culprit!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.82,0:07:16.70,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.54,0:07:22.88,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Honestly! This is a crime scene, not a playground!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.33,0:07:24.20,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Inspector Megure!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.93,0:07:28.82,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We found a coat that looks like the one the killer was wearing
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.82,0:07:32.19,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,in a trash bin between the restroom and the skating rink!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.19,0:07:36.98,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Good. See if Sonoko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}, who witnessed the killer, recognizes it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.98,0:07:38.32,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.92,0:07:41.67,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh... Excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.67,0:07:45.57,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.57,0:07:48.15,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to return our skates.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.15,0:07:51.10,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You can question us after that, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.10,0:07:56.34,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Remember, we've all got alibis. We were all watching the fireworks when it happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.34,0:07:57.51,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.51,0:08:00.75,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Except Oda, who doesn't like fireworks.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.05,0:08:09.78,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so glad I decided to watch them.\NOtherwise, I'd be a suspect too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.78,0:08:11.58,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Izumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.58,0:08:13.35,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it's true, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.15,0:08:18.04,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Okay, time to knock the old man out with a tranquilizer dart...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.26,0:08:21.12,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's end the meaningless probe.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.78,0:08:25.82,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's time to clear everything up.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.82,0:08:28.43,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,After all, the answer's simple!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.43,0:08:31.04,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Has he really...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.04,0:08:34.00,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you figured out who it is?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.00,0:08:38.00,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. And this time I'm certain!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.00,0:08:40.71,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The person who waited for Chihiro{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} in the restroom
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.71,0:08:43.74,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and killed her with the shotgun...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.64,0:08:48.46,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,was you, Kunitomo Oda{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.55,0:08:52.63,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It was you, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.10,0:08:55.45,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.21,0:09:00.03,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, wait a minute! I...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.94,0:09:03.60,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You were up against the wrong man!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.60,0:09:09.49,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You may have tried to fake a dying message in your victim's blood,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.49,0:09:12.31,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,but you couldn't fool me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.31,0:09:15.97,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}You were fooled {\i1}bigtime{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.97,0:09:20.05,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You wrote that yourself after you killed her!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.05,0:09:26.14,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Nobody can write a letter on the wall after being shot through the chest.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.14,0:09:32.24,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And something Izumi Sano{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} said\Njust now cleared everything up for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.24,0:09:38.91,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You tried to frame Sano{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, who you knew usually didn't watch the fireworks,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.91,0:09:45.71,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,by committing the murder at the time the fireworks went up.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.71,0:09:53.13,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You used her gun for the crime and wrote the letter S on the wall in blood!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.04,0:09:57.83,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But unfortunately for you, she decided to watch the fireworks after all,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.83,0:10:02.37,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,leaving you as the only one without an alibi, and your plan collaps—
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.37,0:10:07.46,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, ha-hi-hu-he-ho...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.21,0:10:16.21,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Right. As I was saying,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.21,0:10:19.22,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,the killer wanted to make everyone {\i1}suspect{\i0} Oda{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r},
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.22,0:10:22.59,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and take the {\i1}real{\i0} culprit off the list of suspects.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.59,0:10:25.50,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That was the killer's true aim.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.50,0:10:29.32,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,S-So just who was the killer?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.32,0:10:34.27,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The one who killed Chihiro Itami{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, excluding Oda{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.27,0:10:36.69,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,One of the members of the clay shooting club...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.16,0:10:39.45,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It was you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.80,0:10:48.40,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The one who killed Chihiro Itami{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, excluding Oda{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r},
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.40,0:10:50.65,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,one of the members of the clay shooting club...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.65,0:10:52.25,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It was you,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.25,0:10:53.79,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Izumi Sano{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.04,0:10:59.95,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I-Izumi?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.94,0:11:02.37,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.37,0:11:09.61,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You used your own gun and wrote your\Nown initial on the wall to mislead us.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.67,0:11:13.76,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We were supposed to reason that\Nno killer would leave her own gun
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.76,0:11:16.59,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and write her own initials\Nat the scene of the crime!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.59,0:11:20.65,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Taking advantage of this psychology, you set a trap.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.65,0:11:24.18,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You shot Chihiro in the chest rather than the head
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.18,0:11:28.26,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,to make the letter written in blood seem more plausible.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.26,0:11:33.79,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A person shot in the head\Ncouldn't write a letter on the wall.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.79,0:11:36.00,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.00,0:11:39.93,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I was watching the fireworks with Ran{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}\Nfrom the very beginning, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.93,0:11:45.03,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If the crime was committed when the fireworks went up, there's no way I could've done it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.03,0:11:50.96,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's if the murder was really committed when the fireworks went up.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.96,0:11:52.90,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.90,0:11:58.65,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Sonoko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r} already said the killer was still in the restroom when the fireworks began!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.65,0:11:59.94,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.94,0:12:04.70,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What Sonoko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} heard was the gunshot, not the fireworks.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.35,0:12:07.40,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be silly!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.40,0:12:11.40,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Nobody would mistake a gunshot for a firework going off.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.53,0:12:17.05,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Boom!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.54,0:12:21.97,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, doesn't it sound just like a firework?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.97,0:12:23.17,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Er, yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.17,0:12:25.32,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,B-But how did you do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.03,0:12:27.46,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,With this!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.47,0:12:32.22,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A...five-yen coin?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.22,0:12:37.97,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If you put it against your lips and whistle,\Nit makes the sound louder and huskier,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.97,0:12:41.93,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,like the whistle when a firework goes up!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.41,0:12:48.79,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it, it did sound like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.79,0:12:50.79,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that right, Uncle?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.49,0:12:55.34,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Normally you wouldn't confuse a gunshot with a firework.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.34,0:13:01.50,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But if the gunshot was paired with that whistle at a time when people were expecting fireworks,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.50,0:13:04.10,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,it'd be an easy mistake to make.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.10,0:13:11.74,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,As proof, Sonoko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} said she heard only {\i1}one{\i0} explosion.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.74,0:13:16.22,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The fireworks show here starts with a sequence of {\i1}three{\i0} fireworks, in red, blue and yellow.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.49,0:13:20.31,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that right, Sonoko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-neechan{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.85,0:13:23.39,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.39,0:13:27.67,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But how did the killer know Sonoko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} would be standing outside the restroom?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.67,0:13:30.47,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There were two or three other people there.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.32,0:13:34.69,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the only restroom you can enter with skates on.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.86,0:13:42.00,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She assumed that after she put the sign on the door, some people would wait outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.00,0:13:47.03,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Here's what happened: Sano{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} asked Chihiro{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} to meet her in this restroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.03,0:13:50.05,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She hung the cleaning sign on the door,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.05,0:13:55.85,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,locked it, left to get her shotgun,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.85,0:13:59.19,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,then came back to the restroom where Chihiro{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} was waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.19,0:14:01.03,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She pointed the gun at her,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.03,0:14:04.70,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,waited until a minute or two before the fireworks show,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.70,0:14:08.67,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,whistled through the five-yen coin, and shot her.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.67,0:14:11.85,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Then she used the blood to write her own initial on the wall.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.85,0:14:16.62,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Then she ran back to the skating rink\Nbefore the real fireworks began!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.62,0:14:18.45,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It was all to frame Oda{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r},
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.45,0:14:23.98,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,who wouldn't have an alibi,\Nsince he'd gone off on his own.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.98,0:14:26.74,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey... Is this true, Izumi?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.74,0:14:27.90,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Izumi?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.39,0:14:34.74,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I see... I guess I could have committed the crime that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.74,0:14:36.95,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But why me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.95,0:14:40.17,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The other three could've used the same trick!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.74,0:14:42.00,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Izumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.00,0:14:44.45,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know who you are,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.45,0:14:46.80,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,but I won't take these false accusations!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.90,0:14:50.92,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,KIX.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.14,0:14:55.10,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know what that is?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.57,0:14:59.98,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the gibberish Chihiro typed into her cell phone, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.98,0:15:01.98,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No. It's not gibberish.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.57,0:15:07.63,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,While you had the gun in her mouth,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.63,0:15:11.27,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,she typed a message into her phone from inside her pocket,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.27,0:15:16.20,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,then kept pressing the Send button,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.20,0:15:22.89,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,in the hope that whoever was on her redial would get the message!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.51,0:15:26.79,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Aha!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.79,0:15:30.68,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So that's why the area where the phone number appears was filled with pound signs!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.68,0:15:33.81,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If you keep pressing Send on this phone, it turns into a pound sign.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.49,0:15:38.66,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,T-Then the word on the screen is...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.66,0:15:42.80,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The actual dying message left by the victim!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.51,0:15:45.31,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, so what?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.31,0:15:48.70,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you saying KIX is my name?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.70,0:15:51.50,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been told that Chihiro{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} told all of you...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.06,0:15:57.91,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,that Oda{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} was the odd one out in your group.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.91,0:15:59.96,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What's that got to do with anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.96,0:16:02.27,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The victim is Itami{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.27,0:16:05.50,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The two people behind you are\NKomatsu{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} and Misawa{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.50,0:16:08.83,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And your full name is {\i1}Izumi{\i0} Sano.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.83,0:16:11.31,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Get it now?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.31,0:16:13.94,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Then let me put it this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.94,0:16:18.16,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Your friend, who died in an accident six months ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.05,0:16:21.53,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,His name was Narita{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.23,0:16:23.04,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.04,0:16:25.93,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I got it! Airports!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.93,0:16:30.95,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Apart from Oda{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, everybody's name is the location of an airport!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.95,0:16:34.06,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But I can't recall any airport called Sano, can you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.06,0:16:35.41,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.41,0:16:39.20,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And what does any of this have to do with KIX?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.50,0:16:43.69,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.69,0:16:50.14,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,KIX is the three-letter code to Kansai International Airport!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.14,0:16:55.55,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's in {\i1}Izumisano{\i0} City in Osaka.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.55,0:16:58.19,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Now do you understand,\NIzumi Sano{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.16,0:17:00.13,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,B-But...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.13,0:17:04.53,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The real killer could've left that message to incriminate me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.53,0:17:09.69,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Then if I show you this, it may convince you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.69,0:17:14.58,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Check the bloodstain on the floor near the victim's left toe.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.58,0:17:15.38,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.66,0:17:18.06,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Bloodstain?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.52,0:17:25.55,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,T-This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.01,0:17:30.48,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,When Sano{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} wrote the letter on the wall,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.48,0:17:33.40,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,she accidentally stepped in blood\Nwith the blade of her skate.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.40,0:17:39.45,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She left some blood in the corridor when she escaped.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.45,0:17:42.26,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She hasn't realized...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.26,0:17:47.01,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There are traces of Chihiro{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s blood on the blade of her skate!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.45,0:18:01.33,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I-Izumi...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.69,0:18:06.48,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. Names of airports, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.14,0:18:11.43,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just the kind of thing a pampered girl like her,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.43,0:18:13.99,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,who travels the world on her parents' dime, would think of.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.99,0:18:17.35,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Izumi... You really killed Chihiro?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.35,0:18:19.48,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But... But why?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.66,0:18:22.17,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Narita{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.96,0:18:24.25,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Narita?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.25,0:18:25.37,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.37,0:18:29.00,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I just wanted to get back at Chihiro\Nfor driving Narita{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} to suicide.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.00,0:18:30.61,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Suicide?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.61,0:18:33.57,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But that was an accident...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.96,0:18:38.88,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Chihiro had dumped him that day.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.09,0:18:42.76,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He pulled the trigger himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.49,0:18:48.68,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone thought he had an accident\Nwhile he was cleaning his gun.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.15,0:18:53.80,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I told him she wasn't worth it,\Nbut he was devastated.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.80,0:18:57.15,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But why {\i1}kill{\i0} her?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.15,0:19:00.92,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If that was all there was to it, I could've handled it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.60,0:19:06.49,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But then there was the cheating.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.21,0:19:09.52,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Cheating?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.12,0:19:16.68,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. While I was sick in bed, Narita{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} called.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.68,0:19:19.13,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He said, It's over... We've both been betrayed...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.13,0:19:22.22,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Chihiro and Oda are seeing each other...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.22,0:19:24.60,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He was so broken up.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.55,0:19:28.58,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But Oda was going out with you back then!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.58,0:19:29.89,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.89,0:19:32.49,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And he knew Narita{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}'s feelings,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.49,0:19:36.61,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,but he went ahead and made\Nfools of us with Chihiro!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.61,0:19:37.19,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not true!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.53,0:19:42.62,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It was just one of her lies to make Narita jealous!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.62,0:19:46.25,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Then why didn't you tell that to Narita{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.98,0:19:51.66,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He said he asked you about it,\Nbut you brushed him off!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.17,0:19:56.80,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I'm sorry, but I wasn't paying attention to Narita that day.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.05,0:20:02.50,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I was too worried about you and your illness.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.10,0:20:09.98,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe you should've killed me instead...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.65,0:20:18.21,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll hear the rest at the station.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.26,0:20:23.20,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.30,0:20:27.15,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you wait for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.15,0:20:29.52,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how long it takes...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.52,0:20:32.06,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And how far I may go...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.06,0:20:37.40,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry. I'm a pretty stubborn guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.54,0:20:39.80,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.05,0:22:22.41,Flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.41,0:22:24.45,Flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Can you wait for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.45,0:22:26.55,Flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}No matter how long it takes...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.55,0:22:28.03,Flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}And how far I may go...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.75,0:22:35.85,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You sound like a tired old man.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.34,0:22:39.02,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What? You have no idea how I feel!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.02,0:22:39.80,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, a phone call.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.31,0:22:45.28,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes? Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.28,0:22:48.24,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,Seattle International Karate Championship
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.72,0:22:50.61,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I won, Sonoko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}! I won the winter tournament!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.64,0:22:54.81,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I never thought I'd meet so many tough oppo—
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.81,0:22:55.66,Radio,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}You idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.66,0:22:57.50,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You stupid, stupid idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.50,0:23:01.63,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Why didn't you call me earlier? I sent you my phone number two months ago!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.63,0:23:06.17,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry... I didn't want to call for no reason...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.17,0:23:07.24,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Oh, geez...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.24,0:23:10.71,Radio,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}By the way, Sonoko{\rHonorifics - Radio\be10}-san{\r\be10}, I heard there's a flu bug going around Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.71,0:23:13.30,Radio,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Don't go out in those short skirts.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.62,0:23:18.55,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not! I'm wearing something really long today...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.55,0:23:23.85,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew it! Sonoko got another cell phone\Nto keep in touch with Kyogoku{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.85,0:23:25.23,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.23,0:23:27.22,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A cell phone just for two...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.90,0:23:29.68,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,How nice...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.47,0:23:34.44,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}A few days later,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.64,0:23:40.55,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}I sent Ran a cell phone as a thank-you gift for the sweater.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.02,0:23:44.19,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}She was a little suspicious at first,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.70,0:23:51.01,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}but I think she kind of liked it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.01,0:23:52.16,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Well, I guess that's that...
